title: Get On The Waitlist, Private Patio, Reserved Covered Parking Available
posting_body: ['Regatta Apartments', '1145 South 216th St, Des Moines, WA, 98198', 'Call Now -', 'show contact info', 'x 33', 'OR Text', '33', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to text us.', 'Want more information on this unit?', 'See link (below):', '<URL>', 'The Best in Des Moines Apartment Living', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 2 Bath, approximately 970 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'The Regatta Apartment Homes are situated in a park-like setting with beautifully landscaped grounds, yet just minutes away from all major services.', 'We offer well-designed one and two bedroom homes featuring wood burning fireplaces, in-home washer and dryer, wood style flooring and so much more!', 'Relax in our newly renovated clubhouse and pool or enjoy time on your private patio.', 'The Regatta is conveniently located less than one mile from the Marina, downtown, light rail and major freeways.', 'Pricing and availability is subject to change.', 'Please contact our office for details.', 'Pet Policy', 'Max 2 pets per home.', '$300 refundable deposit & $350 non refundable fee.', '$35 pet rent per pet.', 'No weight limit.', 'Breed restrictions Doberman, Chow-Chow, Siberian Husky, St.', 'Bernard, German Shepherd, Doberman', 'Pinscher, Bull Mastiff, Alaskan Malamute,', 'Akita, Rottweiler, Wolf Hybrids, Presa', 'Canario, Pit Bull (also known as American', 'Staffordshire, American Pit Bull Terrier,', 'Staffordshire Bull Terrier) and all mixes', 'of the above breeds.', 'Aggressive animals,', 'or animals with threatening or violent', 'behavior, is not allowed.', 'Income Requirements:', 'Income 2.5 times the Rent.', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Friday:9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Saturday:10:00AM-5:00PM', 'RkMns2DZ']
